summary: Adds Standalone Samurai Armor of 6 Samurai Clans from History. And 1 special armor in honor of Musashi Miyamoto.
descriptionHtml:
And for those who want a classical samurai Armor check out [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30299] Samurai Genji Armor [/url]

This mod contains standalone armor and weapons for a variety of samurai clans from history.  The colors are a bit flashy but hey this is skyrim.
